      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=ykc4criveg]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ykc4criveg]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=luvkuov1wp]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=luvkuov1wp]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=gjrq2shskj]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gjrq2shskj]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=qs9ktqosll]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=qs9ktqosll]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=fo4rllg77g]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=fo4rllg77g]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=qsc92xxrlw]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=qsc92xxrlw]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=nntudsn67p]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nntudsn67p]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=i5u5hu3n4x]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=i5u5hu3n4x]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=f3euwry8gy]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=f3euwry8gy]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=qnooizmfy3]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=qnooizmfy3]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754711375&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=362\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599162914/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754711375&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"611\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"598933687\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"826076e3-7fbe-4490-9e54-4da6c03d1bad\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754711375&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=611 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754711375&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=362 1x\" /></span><h1 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-WelcometoTheRenderManFundamentals\"><span data-colorid=\"nntudsn67p\">Welcome to The RenderMan Fundamentals</span></h1><p>The RenderMan Fundamentals are designed around hands-on projects to help you on your creative journey.</p><p>With ongoing lesson updates and fun tips and tricks, the RenderMan Fundamentals are designed as quick introductions to get you started. Each section has its own downloadable projects to help you follow along with every lesson.</p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-local-id=\"9db8b4f5-9849-48da-8ec7-4e1fcb571b84\" data-macro-id=\"7a7cb3ece8d03db149614e21d6f304604ac5f055e05ba8ad8f07091ca04463ea\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"300\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/958538528\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"1280\">\n</iframe>\n\n<hr /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h3 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-CreativityFirst\"><span data-colorid=\"qnooizmfy3\">Creativity First</span></h3><p>The RenderMan Fundamentals are presented by Pixar artist Eugene Riecansky, an award-winning artist and director, whose production experience will give your learning process the creative context it deserves.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"36abc317-e9ce-4747-b598-fd23cffbb694.jpg\" width=\"396\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/36abc317-e9ce-4747-b598-fd23cffbb694.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755264714&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=396\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599162914/36abc317-e9ce-4747-b598-fd23cffbb694.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755264714&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"598933696\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"36abc317-e9ce-4747-b598-fd23cffbb694.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"6049e22b-c578-44df-83e1-b8d537a13970\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/36abc317-e9ce-4747-b598-fd23cffbb694.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755264714&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/36abc317-e9ce-4747-b598-fd23cffbb694.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755264714&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=396 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h2 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-RenderManFundamentalsLearningPath\"><span data-colorid=\"qsc92xxrlw\">RenderMan Fundamentals Learning Path</span></h2><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/599228438\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RF_GettingStarted.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_GettingStarted.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755793786&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599162914/RF_GettingStarted.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755793786&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599228512\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RF_GettingStarted.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"505168cd-3e67-469a-9cc8-efbd9436fc38\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_GettingStarted.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755793786&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_GettingStarted.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755793786&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-GettingStarted\"><span data-colorid=\"gjrq2shskj\">Getting Started</span></h1><p>Welcome newbie! </p><p>From installation to your first render, this introduction is for you.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/599425025\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RF_ocio2.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_ocio2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757756165637&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599162914/RF_ocio2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757756165637&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"598933703\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RF_ocio2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"120f7b40-c5c8-41e5-992e-e671604c834e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_ocio2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757756165637&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_ocio2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757756165637&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-ColorManagement\"><span data-colorid=\"i5u5hu3n4x\">Color Management</span></h1><p>Let's demystify Aces color management, part of the Academy's OCIO system.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/599523329\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RF_materials.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_materials.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755941014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599162914/RF_materials.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755941014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599228526\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RF_materials.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"e0cbc191-d836-4ddc-ad30-6c72132dd6c7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_materials.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755941014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_materials.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757755941014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-Materials-PxrSurface\"><span data-colorid=\"f3euwry8gy\">Materials - PxrSurface</span></h1><p>Learn about making photorealistic materials with the stunning PxrSurface.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/600113153\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RF_lama.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_lama.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757846775855&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599162914/RF_lama.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757846775855&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599163105\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RF_lama.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"ff7b3f63-d3a8-47a2-b10c-3bca80d7196e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_lama.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757846775855&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_lama.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757846775855&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-Materials-Lama\"><span data-colorid=\"luvkuov1wp\">Materials - Lama</span></h1><p>Learn the basics of the incredible layering shading system, Lama, from the folks at ILM.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/599523361\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RF_patterns.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_patterns.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757756041531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599162914/RF_patterns.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757756041531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599097468\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RF_patterns.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"c4267303-5a22-4c4c-973b-699cd8246c52\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_patterns.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757756041531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_patterns.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757756041531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-Patterns\"><span data-colorid=\"qs9ktqosll\">Patterns</span></h1><p>Expand photorealism through the use of procedural nodes and textures.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/599523393\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RF_ocio.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_ocio.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757756071787&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599162914/RF_ocio.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757756071787&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599228519\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RF_ocio.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"c70458ab-a50a-4031-8895-256352bd9f3e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_ocio.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757756071787&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/RF_ocio.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757756071787&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-Lighting\"><span data-colorid=\"fo4rllg77g\">Lighting</span></h1><p>Let's play cinematographer in Solaris and learn about Pixar's lighting toolset.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/568754187\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"STRONGIMAGE.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/STRONGIMAGE.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754706428&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599162914/STRONGIMAGE.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754706428&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"598933680\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"STRONGIMAGE.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"7b632fa5-d16d-4905-b94e-4b87c8f0f908\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/STRONGIMAGE.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754706428&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599162914/STRONGIMAGE.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757754706428&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-Rendering\"><span data-colorid=\"ykc4criveg\">Rendering</span></h1><p>Coming Soon &hellip;.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h2 id=\"RenderManFundamentals-&quot;TheRenderManfundamentalvideosareagoodbasistogetanoverviewofPixar'sownrenderengineandhelptodiscovermoreofthispowerfulrenderer.&quot;\"><em>&quot;The RenderMan fundamental videos are a good basis to get an overview of Pixar's own render engine and help to discover more of this powerful renderer.&quot;</em><br /></h2><p><em>Johnny Fehr, Texture &amp; Lookdev Artist</em></p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
